1.4
log
@Reduce libm's exports and make internal calls go direct.
All dependencies on libc are now via reserved/standardized names.

ok kettenis@@ millert@@ deraadt@@
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: fenv.c,v 1.3 2014/04/18 15:09:52 guenther Exp $	*/

/*
